A burst of colours, tradition, and couture 🌼✨
Appliqué multicolour florals meet a luxe designer crop and a fluid attached drape—crafted for the modern muse at her Haldi celebration designed by @kanchanguptaofficial @kanchans_  Radiate elegance, grace, and festive joy in every thread. 💛🌸

Mehendi vibes, but make it couture!
A riot of colors, a burst of tradition — these stunning mehendi looks are designed by @kanchanguptaofficial for the modern bride who loves to stand out.
Each outfit in this reel tells its own story in hues of joy, love, and celebration — from bold greens to sunshine yellows and playful purples.
And yes, that’s the queen herself  in black, styling magic into every thread
